
---

## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.so

# Virtual environment
venv/
.venv/
env/
ENV/

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Testing / cache
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# Build files
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Local secrets
.env

# Coverage
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Torch / large temp files
*.pt
*.pth

# Optional dataset or output folders
data/
outputs/
checkpoints/